      </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 24px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; font-weight: bold; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/738338870/T2RernXfNaXXXXXXXX_!!738338870.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<div style=\"border-bottom: rgb(170,196,229) 1px solid; border-left: rgb(170,196,229) 1px solid; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(170,196,229); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px auto; width: 750px; font: 14px/26px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); overflow: hidden; border-top: rgb(170,196,229) 1px solid; border-right: rgb(170,196,229) 1px solid; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><br />\r\n<font style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51)\">测试仪</font>器：Spyder Elite 3校色仪</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;接下来，我们要做的是使用Spyder Elite 3校色仪来制作出这款机型的原始icc文件，并将其进行分析得出AOC E2251FW的色彩特性表现。<span style=\"color: rgb(255,0,0)\"><font color=\"#c00000\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">下面图片中白色的闭合曲线代表sRGB色彩空间，红色的闭合曲线<font color=\"#c00000\">代表AOC E2251FW</font>色彩空间。</strong></font></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"AOC\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px; border-left: 1px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 1px; border-right: 1px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://2b.zol-img.com.cn/product/66_500x2000/315/ce5Vsm4peuuE.jpg\" /><br />\r\nAOC E2251FW液晶的色彩特性<br />\r\n（红色部分为AOC E2251FW色彩空间，白色部分为sRGB色彩空间）</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 在上图中，理论上而言，红色的区域如果完全覆盖白色的sRGB色彩空间是最为理想的。而通过上面的图片，我们可以看到代表AOC E2251FW色彩空间覆盖了整个sRGB色彩空间。它对于绝大部分色彩都能够十分丰富的表现出来。总体来说，它的表现十分出色。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 22px\">●&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"line-height: 22px; font-weight: 700\">覆盖sRGB色彩空间的意义</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/22px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; sRGB色彩空间是惠普与微软一起开发的用于<font style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51)\">显示器</font>、<font style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51)\">打印机</font>以及因特网的一种标准RGB色彩空间，它定义了红色、绿色与蓝色三原色的颜色，即在其它两种颜色值都为零时该颜色的最大值。因此若显示器能够完全包含sRGB色域，说明它能够完全胜任普通的摄影以及打印工作，色彩显示会更加准确，并且不会出现无法显示的颜色。而如果显示器无法完全涵盖sRGB色彩空间，说明这款显示器会无法正常显示部分颜色。若参考更多详细信息，请详见《<font color=\"#000099\">编辑教你怎样判断液晶显示器色彩好坏</font>》一文。</p>\r\n<div style=\"border-bottom: rgb(194,217,242) 1px dotted; padding-bottom: 4px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); margin-top: 20px; text-indent: 0px; padding-left: 5px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 20px; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"float: right\">产品：</span><span style=\"float: right\">E2251FW&nbsp;AOC&nbsp;液晶显示器&nbsp;<img alt=\"回到顶部阅读\" align=\"absMiddle\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px\" src=\"http://icon.zol.com.cn/doc/2010/top.png\" /></span>\r\n<h2 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px\">AOC两用新品LED屏幕均匀性测试</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">●&nbsp;<strong style=\"font-weight: 700\"><font style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51)\">AOC</font></strong><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">两用新品LED屏幕均匀性测试</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 接下来，我们就对AOC&nbsp;<font style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51)\">E2251FW</font>进行屏幕均匀性方面的测试，首先是屏幕亮度均匀性测试。下面大家看到的测试方法和测试结果是我们ZOL<font style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51)\">显示器</font>频道在2011年推出的全新内容，测试的内容也将更加精准，更加客观，并且将会广泛的应用在今后的测试文章中。</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 屏幕亮度均匀性的测试同样借助Spyder 3 Elite校色仪来完成，我们将屏幕划分为9个大区域，分布测试计算其屏幕在全白、全黑时的亮度以及色度坐标，最终得出以下的结论。（以下结果均在IRE输出达100%，即使用最大亮度和对比度输出时进行测试）</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><br style=\"line-height: 0; font-size: 0px\" />\r\n<br />\r\nAOC E2251FW在9个区域的亮度数据和与中心点亮度的差异<br />\r\n（差异越小，代表越均匀）</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','images/201311/thumb_img/1704_thumb_G_1384741867836.jpg','images/201311/goods_img/1704_G_1384741867640.jpg','images/201311/source_img/1704_G_1384741867035.jpg','1','','1','1','0','0','1367274021','100','0','0','0','0','0','0','1398294237','6','','1','0','0','0');
